title: [Boreas Ridge, Norte Court]
description: The path ends here, carved amongst great shelves of brilliant sunset-hued layered rock.  A sheltered outcropping supports a small family of trees.  Beautifully carved statues formed from the local rock guard the ornate gates of invar and manicured private grounds.
